Revision history for Plack-Middleware-Text-Minify:

v0.4.1    2023-10-28 09:34:02+01:00 Europe/London
  [Tests]
  - Migrated tests to use Test2.

  - Removed use of Test::Most.

  [Other]
  - Bumped the minimum version of Text::Minify::XS to v0.7.0.

v0.4.0    2023-05-10 08:58:43+01:00 Europe/London
  [Incompatible Changes]
  - Upgraded the minimum Perl version to v5.14.

v0.3.3    2023-05-08 10:28:54+01:00 Europe/London
  [Documentation]
  - Explicitly documented the support policy for older Perl versions.

  [Other]
  - Updateed MANIFEST.SKIP rules.

v0.3.2    2022-06-10 16:26:00+01:00 Europe/London
  [Bug Fixes]
