    with undef data.

  [Documentation]
  - Bump copyright year.

v0.3.1    2022-03-19 10:56:57+00:00 Europe/London
  [Enhancements]
  - Improve the performance for non-IO::Handle bodies.

v0.3.0    2022-03-16 15:38:02+00:00 Europe/London
  [Enhancements]
